  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Kitchen Staff/Helper",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist in basic food preparation and cooking</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen</p></li><li><p>Wash and organize utensils, equipment, and work areas</p></li><li><p>Help with inventory and stock management</p></li><li><p>Follow kitchen safety and hygiene procedures</p></li><li><p>Support chefs and senior kitchen staff in daily operations</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate in basic English</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and hardworking</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn and follow instructions</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Prior kitchen experience is a plus but not required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Monthly salary <strong>SGD 1,800 – 2,200</strong></p></li><li><p>Training and guidance provided</p></li><li><p>Supportive team environment</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to learn kitchen operations and develop skills</p></li><li><p>Potential for career growth within the kitchen team</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Shortlisted candidates will be contacted for a brief phone discussion, followed by instructions for joining the team.</p>",
